Trait rerun::external::eframe::egui::epaint::emath::Numeric

pub trait Numeric: Clone + Copy + PartialEq + PartialOrd + 'static {
    const INTEGRAL: bool;
    const MIN: Self;
    const MAX: Self;

    // Required methods
    fn to_f64(self) -> f64;
    fn from_f64(num: f64) -> Self;
}
